What we do"

We record the talks from your event and turn them into a high quality podcast series.

Plenary sessions, Interviews, words from your sponsors - all can be used to create an engaging podcast series for your community.

"Why Capture"

Events are more than just a day. We believe an event should provide you with enough content to keep your community buzzing for months.

Thats why at Lime Capture were focused on helping you generate rich, high quality content to increase the value of the your brand and event.





